        "content": "<p>I am doing a proof by cases with a match statement , and three of my cases have exactly the same proof. However, I can't figure out how to combine it and only write that proof once.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/S1HFE9uPp05OIZ7NGYbagiJx/image.png\">image.png</a> </p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/S1HFE9uPp05OIZ7NGYbagiJx/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/3121/S1HFE9uPp05OIZ7NGYbagiJx/image.png\"></a></div><p>I tried using wildcards, but that did not work.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/Iu6ScbWvkvl0oKB1sNTKRN4R/image.png\">image.png</a> </p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/Iu6ScbWvkvl0oKB1sNTKRN4R/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/3121/Iu6ScbWvkvl0oKB1sNTKRN4R/image.png\"></a></div><p>The match does recognize that these are the three cases that need to be solved if I omit them.<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/W9aHlY72xv3V36KNnn7eviv2/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/W9aHlY72xv3V36KNnn7eviv2/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/3121/W9aHlY72xv3V36KNnn7eviv2/image.png\"></a></div>",
